      &lt;img alt="Photos of several gadgets, nuclear power plants, Donald Trump, and more with a Vergecast illustration" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_MVfpQ1qEEc2wA3AUpbSWzxGl7I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73754932/VST_1129_Site.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Alex Parkin / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
